        <tr><td>Gear transmission rebuild on-site</td><td>$1,400 to $2,400</td></tr>
        <tr><td>On/off switch replacement</td><td>$140 to $260</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Multi-component repair (aged HL units)</td><td>$1,200 to $2,800</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Heritage Legacy refurbishment</td><td>$1,800 to $3,400</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty (SDAR labor)</td><td>90 days parts and labor</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-number">Related</p>
    <h2>Commercial smallwares service across the catalog.</h2>
    <div class="related-grid">
      <a href="/commercial/mixer-repair/" class="related-card"><h3>Commercial Mixer Repair Hub</h3><p>Parent pillar. Hobart Legacy plus Univex, Varimixer spiral, KitchenAid Commercial coverage.</p></a>
